The highest power produced was 93.9 mW, observed when the arm was straight down (mimicking standing) and the sleeve was receiving direct sunlight. Conversely, the lowest power was 13.5 mW, observed when the arm was up and angled at 90 ∘\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
